OL,3,CEx-officer can't remember call he made
OL,4,Cto Robert Hamill murder suspect
OL,6,FA Craigavon court has heard how two
OL,7,F"entirely innocent" people were
OL,8,Fsentenced over a former police
OL,9,Fofficer's cover up of phone-calls made
OL,10,Fto a suspect in a sectarian murder
OL,11,Fcase.
OL,13,FRobert Cecil Atkinson, 71 and of
OL,14,FBrownstone Road in Portadown, is
OL,15,Fcharged with conspiring to pervert the
OL,16,Fcourt of justice in the investigation
OL,17,Finto a gang attack on Robert Hamill in
OL,18,FPortadown in 1997.
OL,20,FRobert Hamill was brutally attacked by
OL,21,Fa loyalist mob after a night out.
