OL,6,FAn RUC vehicle with four officers
OL,7,Finside was yards away, and this crew
OL,8,Fhas previously been accused of failing
OL,9,Fto intervene.
OL,11,FThe young catholic man, a father of
OL,12,Fthree, succumbed to his injuries over
OL,13,Fa week later.
OL,15,FRetired RUC reservist Robert Cecil
OL,16,FAtkinson was one of those in the
OL,17,Fpolice vehicle that night.
