OL,3,CEx-officer can't remember call he made
OL,4,Cto Robert Hamill murder suspect
OL,6,FHe pleaded guilty to conspiring to
OL,7,Fpervert the course of justice in
OL,8,FApril. This related to phone calls
OL,9,Fmade to a young man who was at the
OL,10,Fcrime scene, and would become a
OL,11,Fsuspect.
OL,13,FInitially he told police he did not
OL,14,Fmake any calls to the suspect.
OL,16,FInvestigations then revealed that two
OL,17,Fcalls were made - one hours after the
OL,18,Fattack, and one the next week on May
OL,19,F2nd.
