OL,3,CEx-officer can't remember call he made
OL,4,Cto Robert Hamill murder suspect
OL,6,FHe later said it was a couple who
OL,7,Fstayed with him that night, to check
OL,8,Fin on their niece who was a girlfriend
OL,9,Fof the suspect.
OL,11,FThe second call was allegedly his wife
OL,12,Fwho called the suspect on "matters
OL,13,Frelating to martial arts".
OL,15,FProsecuting KC Toby Hedworth told the
OL,16,Fcourt that the couple's relationship
OL,17,Flater broke down and it emerged that
OL,18,FAtkinson had drawn the married couple
OL,19,Finto his coverup.
