OL,3,CEx-officer can't remember call he made
OL,4,Cto Robert Hamill murder suspect
OL,6,FThey were then charged themselves, and
OL,7,Fsentenced to six months each back in
OL,8,F2002 - he was jailed, while her
OL,9,Fsentence was suspended.
OL,11,FThe prosecution admitted they can't
OL,12,Fsay what was said in that phone call,
OL,13,Fbut that the court is entitled to draw
OL,14,Fan inference.
OL,16,FDefence KC Barry Gibson told Craigavon
OL,17,FCourt Court that due to multiple
OL,18,Fstrokes, TMIs and heart attacks, "he
OL,19,Fcannot recall" the contents of the
OL,20,Fcall he made on 27 April 1997.
