OL,3,CEx-officer can't remember call he made
OL,4,Cto Robert Hamill murder suspect
OL,6,FJudge Patrick Lynch KC "there is one
OL,7,Fperson in this room who knows what was
OL,8,Fsaid and it's not me or you and no one
OL,9,Felse seems to know."
OL,11,FMr Hedworth KC conceded that while the
OL,12,Fprosecution cannot say what was talked
OL,13,Fabout "however one has to
OL,14,Fcontextualise the call being made by
OL,15,Fan officer who was on duty at the
OL,16,Ftime, who had been present at the time
OL,17,Fof the assault and was ringing a young
OL,18,Fman who was going to be a suspect in
OL,19,Fthe assault and who was also present
OL,20,Fat the time."
