OL,3,CEx-officer can't remember call he made
OL,4,Cto Robert Hamill murder suspect
OL,6,FThe judge further suggested to Mr
OL,7,FGibson that given the significance of
OL,8,Fthe event and the fact that Atkinson
OL,9,F"has been living with this for 27
OL,10,Fyears it seems very improbable that
OL,11,Fsuch an event will have been excised
OL,12,Ffrom his mind," and said that the fact
OL,13,FAtkinson was a serving officer at the
OL,14,Ftime "really does exacerbate the
OL,15,Fgravity" of the situation.
OL,17,FMr Hedworth KC reminded the court that
OL,18,Fthe couple initially believed to have
OL,19,Fmade the phone-call to the suspect
OL,20,Fwere sentenced in 2002.
